content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 21.18 - Commercial food processing establishment

State Regulations

Commercial food processing establishment means any
facility other than a milk plant, to which fluid milk products and fluid cream
products are disposed of that uses such receipts as ingredients in food
products and has no disposition of fluid milk products or fluid cream products
other than those received in consumer-type packages (one gallon or
less). Notes
